Sophiag1
London, UK260 contributions
Overnight stay on a Junk on Halong Bay
The Junk we stayed on was called The Victory.
It was clean and the staff were very friendly. Food they serve was very plentiful and good.
The bedrooms were compacted and had all you needed. The beds were very hard but for an overnight stay it wasn’t too bad.
The view of Halong bay is breath taking and would recommend to anyone to go there.
Went to the cave and went on a boat to see some of Halong. If you wanted to you could kayak.
Breath taking scenery.
