BrakiWorldTraveler
Belgrade, Serbia17,760 contributions
Majestic even in lousy weather
Jan 2024 • Family
This was my second visit to Halong Bay.
First, in 2017 was in postcard like weather with blue skies and big heat.
This January visit was in a bad weather - rain, mist and chilly with only 13-14 'C. However, I enjoyed it very much and such weather even made a mystic and romantic feeling sailing through this worldwide unique nature wonder.
I think you cannot go wrong with any agency you choose. More or less their itinerary is pretty much the same, only the food options differ. So, just do it and enjoy.
